{"tid":690948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又飲大o左]唐英年倡香港資本市場用人民幣結算","createTime":"2018-06-05T09:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T10:23:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c35ba8af27c571ebd0a9a3b2850fb4bbfe04b27","tid":690948,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00001/1528188646064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00001%2F1528188646064&d=X3RJmpT%2FhfxEqYimeumNstZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=2e632c4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00001%2F1528188646064&h=12ca8c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00001/1528188646064</a><br />\n<br />\n前政務司長、政協唐英年表示，本港資本市場可以鼓勵使用人民幣計價、結算等，助人民幣國際化。<br />\n<br />\n唐英年出席活動時表示，今年是本港發展離岸人民幣15年，隨着國家金融政策開放，人民幣國際化愈來愈快，境外人民幣市場逐步完善。而香港是境外第一及最大人民幣離岸中心，現時擁有6000億人民幣資金池，人民幣每日平均成交超過9000億元。<br />\n<br />\n唐英年認為，可利用粵港澳大灣區契機推動跨境人民幣，香港亦扮演「中國曼哈頓」角色，帶動大灣區發展。他又建議推動香港資本市場使用人民幣，鼓勵使用人民幣計價、結算等，助人民幣國際化。"},{"pid":"c80ac5c002140122f512239cbe3d224a5712e4f6","tid":690948,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09fe0d2fcba1c6ccff96391deb9158141a8d906","tid":690948,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:33:47.000Z","msg":"佢家族公司全部用冥幣先講啦"},{"pid":"58f1e6c7ecc87810c697f27d1a70aed4d6ab4798","tid":690948,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"直接取消港紙啦"},{"pid":"0f914fd9b2c8d27abeea8a920d698196f1abdb6d","tid":690948,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike